sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Look Graph Webview
participant Router as GraphMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as RemoveWorktreeUseCase
participant Repository as GitRepository
participant Worktree as Worktree
participant Plans as OperationPlanRegistry

User->>App: Remove linked worktree
App->>Router: remove request(repoLocator, worktreeLocator)
Router->>Registry: resolve repository and worktree
Registry-->>Router: Repository and Worktree
Router->>UseCase: plan(repository, worktree)
alt Worktree is main checkout
  UseCase-->>Router: validation error
  Router-->>App: graph/error(validationFailed)
else Linked worktree
  UseCase->>Repository: listWorktrees()
  UseCase->>Worktree: getStatus()
  UseCase->>Plans: store removeWorktree plan with dirty preview
  Router-->>App: guarded operation plan
  alt User chooses repair stale metadata
    App->>Router: repair request(repoLocator, path)
    Router->>Repository: repairWorktree(path)
    Router-->>App: refresh requested
  else User confirms removal
    App->>Router: guarded acknowledgement(planId)
    Router->>Plans: validate acknowledgement
    Router->>UseCase: execute(validated plan)
    UseCase->>Repository: removeWorktree(path, force)
    Router-->>App: operation success and refresh requested
  end
end
